gn2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 1, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1018168, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "The author says: Late Sayed Ibn Taaoos (r) has written too much about the farewell of Ramazan al-Mubarak, some of which may be stated hereunder. He says: You claim that in some of those farewell the departing of the month of Ramazan has made you sorrowful because you could not be benefitted fully from its blessings. So it is expected from you to be truthful in your claim, you should be truthful in your claim, your face should look melancholic and there should be no sign of falsehood and looseness of character in your conversation during the last days. It is there in the duties of the Shias rather in the nation of the Holy Prophet (s) that they should be fearful of the Almighty Allah and they should be mournful for the delayed reappearance of Hazrat Imam Mahdi (atfs) which was predicted by his honorable forefather the Holy Prophet (s) and we could have achieved the blessings through his medium if he (a) would have existed amongst us. There is a couplet in this regard…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Marhoom Sayed Ibne Taaoos (r) ne bohot kuchh likkha hai Ramazan-ul Mubarak ke dua’e wida par. Unho’n ne daawa kiya hai keh kuchh Mahe Ramazan ki dua’e wida se gham taari hota hai kyu’n keh uski ne’mat ka mukammal faaida nahin utha sake’n. To ummeed hai keh tum apne daawe mein khare utro’n, tumhaara chehra ghamgeen ho aur Mahe Ramazan ke aakhri dino mein jhoot wa bad-akhlaqi ki koi jhalak tumhari ghuftagu mein nazar na aaye. Shiyo’n par laazim hai keh Rasool’e Khuda (s) ki ummat hone ke naate woh Allah (swt) se khouf zadah rahe aur girya kare Hazrat Imam Mahdi (atfs) ki ghaibat par jiski aagaayi unke Jadd Rasool’e Khuda (a) ne ki thi, keh agar Imam’e Waqt (atfs) hamare darmiyan mein hote to un ke zariye se ham Allah (swt) ki ne’mato’n ka ziyadah se ziyadah faaida haasil kar paate. Is silsile mein yeh ek sher…", "UrduDescription": "مرحوم سید ابن طاؤس نے رمضان المبارک کی دعائے وداع پر بہت کچھ لکھا ہے ، اُنہوں نے دعوی کیا ہے کہ کچھ ماہ رمضان کی دعائے وداع سے غم تاری ہوتا ہے کیونکہ اُس کی نعمت کا مکمل فائدہ ہم نہیں اُٹھا سکیں۔ تو اُمید ہے کہ تم اپنے دعوے میں کھرے اُترو، تمہارا چہرا غمگین ہو اور ماہ رمضان کے آخری دنوں میں جھوٹ و بداخلاقی کی کوئی جھلک تمہاری گفتگو میں نظر نہ آئے۔شیعوں پر لازم ہے کہ رسول خداؐ کی اُمت ہونے کے ناتے وہ اللہ تعالی سے خوف زداہ رہیں اور گریہ کریں حضرت امام مہدیؑ کی غیبت پر جس کی آگائی اُن کے جد رسول خداؐ نے کی تھی، کہ اگر امام وقتؑ ہمارے درمیان میں ہوتے تو اُن کے ذریعے سے ہم اللہ تعالی کی نعمتوں کا زیادہ سے زیادہ فائدہ حاصل کر پاتے۔ اس سلسلہ میں یہ ایک شر۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 1, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1018169, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "I am searching with my eyes in every corner of the city but I am unable to see the face of my friend whose face I wanted to see.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Mai apni aankho’n se shaher ki har galiyo’n mein dhoond raha hu, magar mai apne dost ka chehra nahin dekh paata hu jiske chehre ko mai dekhna chahta hu.", "Urdu": "میں اپنی آنکھوں سے شہر کی ہر گلیوں میں ڈھونڈ رہا ہو، مگر میں اپنے دوست کا چہرا نہیں دیکھ پاتا ہوں جس کے چہرے کو میں دیکھنا چاہتا ہوں۔", "RArabic": "O-RADDE-DO TARFEE FID-DEYAARE FALAA ARAA, WAJOO-HO A-HIBBAAA-E-YAD DEENE O-REED.", "ArabicText1": "اُرَدِّدُ طَرْفِيْ فِيْ الدِّيَارِ فَلَا اَرٰی، وَجُوْہُ اَحِبَّآئِیَ الدِّیْنِ اُرِیْدُ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1018170, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "In fact the occultation of Imam Mahdi (atfs) is more severe upon the religious persons than the deprevation of the month of Ramazan. This disappearance from a kind father or a helping brother or an obedient son must be the cause of anguish and distraction and which could be disheartening. Although there is no comparison in their existence and the existence of Hazrat Imam Mahdi (atfs) because he (atfs) is the successor of the Holy Prophet (s) and is the Imam of Hazrat Isa (a) in the Namaz and sovereignty. And he (atfs) is the dispenser of disturbances and tribulations and the rectifier of the matters of all the persons living under the sky.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Dar haqeeqat ek mazhabi shakhs ke liye Imam Mahdi (atfs) ki ghaibat ka dard shadeed hota hai ba-nisbat Mahe Ramzan ke rukhsat hone par. Yeh ghaibat ka dard ek maher-baan baap ke, ya ek madad-gaar bhai ke, ya ek farman bardaar bete ke dur hone par jo dil mein be-chaini hoti hai woh kaifiyat taari hoti hai. Haala’n keh un logo’n ka wujood aur Hazrat Imam Mahdi (atfs) ke wujood mein koi muqaabla nahin hai, is liye keh woh (atfs) Rasool’e Khuda (s) ke ja-nasheen hai aur Hazrat Essa (a) ke bhi Imam hai. Aur woh (atfs) har pareshaani aur mushkilo’n ko hal karne waale aur aasmaan ke neeche tamaam makhlooq ke haadi hai.", "UrduDescription": "در حقیقت ایک مذہبی شخص کے لئے امام مہدیؑ کی غیبت کا درد شدید ہوتا ہے بہ نسبت ماہ رمضان کے رخصت ہونے پر۔ یہ غیبت کا درد ایک مہربان باپ کے، یا ایک مددگار بھائی کے، یا ایک فرمان بردار بیٹے کے دور ہونے پر جو دل میں بےچینی ہوتی ہے وہ کیفیت طاری ہوتی ہے۔  ہالانکہ اُن لوگوں کا وجود اور حضرت امام مہدیؑ کے وجود میں کوئی مقابلہ نہیں ہے، اس لئے کہ وہ (امامؑ) رسول خداؐ کے جانشین ہیں اور حضرت عیسیؑ کے بھی امام ہیں، اور وہ (امامؑ) ہر پریشانی اور مشکلوں کو حل کرنے والے اور آسمان کے نیچے تمام مخلوق کے ہادی ہیں۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1":